# Copy this file to `.env` and paste your own Gemini API key.
# The `.env` file is gitignored — do NOT commit your real key.
#
# Get a free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
#
# Vite only exposes environment variables prefixed with `VITE_` to
# client-side code, so the name below MUST stay as VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY.
# If you rename it, the translator will fail to read it.
#
# Note: because this app has no backend, the key is bundled into the
# JS served to your browser. That's fine for local / classroom use, but
# do not deploy this publicly with your key baked in.

VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
